comments: Allen (CLE) makes marginal contact with Bridges (PHX) as he brushes his body with his arm and does not affect his ability to defend in the post.
Bridges (PHX) makes contact with Allen's (CLE) arm that affects his FOM after securing the loose ball.
Sexton (CLE) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Booker (PHX) gets drawn in the air and as he lands makes marginal contact with Osman's (CLE) body during his shot attempt near the rim.
Booker (PHX) briefly grasps Garland's (CLE) arm during the screen and does not affect his FOM.
Allen (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Booker (PHX) and absorbs the incoming contact.
Booker (PHX) makes contact with Okoro's (CLE) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Osman (CLE) as he collapses his arm and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Ayton (PHX) slightly extends is leg in Okoro's (CLE) path during the screen and does not affect his ability to defend.
Okoro (CLE) moves laterally along Booker's (PHX) path and makes marginal contact to his body during the driving shot attempt.
Allen (CLE) slightly extends his arm into Craig's (PHX) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position during the screen.
Bridges (PHX) makes marginal contact with Okoro's (CLE) body at the start of his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Bridges (PHX) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Okoro (CLE) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Sexton (CLE) legally contests Booker (PHX) jump shot attempt.
